7 An Act relating to public retirement systems;
amending 62 O.S. 2021, Section 3103, as last amended
8 by Section 127, Chapter 452, O.S.L. 2024 (62 O.S.
Supp. 2025, Section 3103), which relates to the
9 Oklahoma Pension Legislation Actuarial Analysis Act;
modifying definition; amending 70 O.S. 2021, Section
10 17-103, as amended by Section 2, Chapter 300, O.S.L.
2024 (70 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 17-103), which
11 relates to membership; modifying provisions related
to certain employees of the Department of Career and
12 Technology Education; and providing effective dates.
